WEBVTT

00:01:55.439 --> 00:01:58.079
I'm with Xiaowei. Is that shameful?

00:01:59.040 --> 00:02:01.640
I live my own life. Is that shameful?

00:02:02.140 --> 00:02:05.219
I, Yang Xiaofang, am pregnant. Is that shameful?

00:02:05.219 --> 00:02:06.099
Is it shameful?

00:02:07.920 --> 00:02:10.080
If I can have this baby, I can raise it.

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:12.659
I own my choices.

00:02:13.460 --> 00:02:14.599
Is it shameful?

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:19.199
I, Yang Xiaofang, am pregnant. Is that shameful?

00:02:19.400 --> 00:02:20.300
Is it shameful?

00:02:22.020 --> 00:02:24.099
I, Yang Xiaofang, am pregnant.

00:02:25.319 --> 00:02:26.740
It's not shameful.

00:02:27.139 --> 00:02:28.560
It's not shameful.

00:02:43.060 --> 00:02:44.080
Uncle.

00:02:44.080 --> 00:02:45.800
Why didn't you go after Xiaowei?

00:02:47.080 --> 00:02:48.259
I'm a scholar.

00:02:48.740 --> 00:02:49.680
They're the warriors.

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:51.000
I've got my dignity.

00:02:52.780 --> 00:02:54.240
Are you afraid you can't beat Xiaowei?

00:02:54.759 --> 00:02:55.539
I've been training.

00:02:55.539 --> 00:02:56.400
Me? Afraid of him?

00:02:58.639 --> 00:02:59.219
Listen, let me tell you.

00:02:59.219 --> 00:02:59.759
Once I get home,

00:02:59.759 --> 00:03:00.740
I'm definitely gonna get attacked.

00:03:00.860 --> 00:03:01.759
You've gotta protect me.

00:03:01.819 --> 00:03:03.900
Don't worry. Leave it to me. I've got you.

00:03:19.580 --> 00:03:19.960
Brother.

00:03:20.780 --> 00:03:22.300
Your house still isn't fixed up.

00:03:22.539 --> 00:03:22.939
The roof.

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:25.680
I've fixed it a few times.

00:03:25.960 --> 00:03:27.099
Still not quite right, huh?

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:28.599
Alright.

00:03:28.879 --> 00:03:29.620
In a couple of days,

00:03:30.300 --> 00:03:31.740
I'll fix it up again.

00:03:32.060 --> 00:03:33.419
Every problem in this world

00:03:33.419 --> 00:03:34.680
Is a leftover from the past.

00:03:35.199 --> 00:03:36.379
By the time you spot the anthill,

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:38.319
The dam's already about to burst.

00:03:39.219 --> 00:03:39.780
Right.

00:03:40.120 --> 00:03:41.500
By the time you see the big belly,

00:03:42.280 --> 00:03:43.780
That baby's about to burst out too.

00:03:45.180 --> 00:03:45.960
What are you saying?

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:53.860
Smells amazing.

00:03:56.620 --> 00:03:57.000
You guys...

00:03:57.759 --> 00:03:59.259
You've all been so busy.

00:03:59.259 --> 00:03:59.719
Give it here, give it here.

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:01.099
Over this whole thing,

00:04:01.159 --> 00:04:02.080
I had to call you all back.

00:04:03.099 --> 00:04:03.879
I feel bad about it.

00:04:03.900 --> 00:04:04.300
Brother.

00:04:04.699 --> 00:04:05.659
What are you talking about?

00:04:06.139 --> 00:04:06.659
What could be

00:04:07.180 --> 00:04:08.539
More important than family?

00:04:10.300 --> 00:04:10.740
Exactly.

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:12.379
I've got plenty of free time anyway.

00:04:12.620 --> 00:04:13.539
I don't have anything going on.

00:04:14.020 --> 00:04:16.680
You all love red kidney beans, right?

00:04:17.819 --> 00:04:19.660
I'll add extra for you today.

00:04:20.120 --> 00:04:20.680
Thanks, brother.

00:04:22.519 --> 00:04:23.160
Today,

00:04:23.560 --> 00:04:24.680
I'll make everyone

00:04:25.079 --> 00:04:25.720
Crispy pork bits

00:04:26.180 --> 00:04:27.079
With diced potatoes.

00:04:28.379 --> 00:04:29.319
Xiaofang's favorite, right?

00:04:30.420 --> 00:04:31.319
Thanks, Auntie.

00:04:32.839 --> 00:04:33.800
Sis, stir-fry some cured pork for me.

00:04:34.519 --> 00:04:35.600
Your face looks like cured pork.

00:04:36.220 --> 00:04:37.000
Drool over it and starve.

00:05:11.139 --> 00:05:11.939
Old man

00:05:12.959 --> 00:05:13.660
This year,

00:05:13.959 --> 00:05:15.259
Thanks to our granddaughter,

00:05:16.019 --> 00:05:16.740
Even with you,

00:05:16.939 --> 00:05:18.660
All seven of us

00:05:18.759 --> 00:05:20.300
Are finally together.

00:05:21.199 --> 00:05:21.779
Grandma,

00:05:22.519 --> 00:05:23.360
Eight of us.

00:05:23.920 --> 00:05:24.420
Right, right, right.

00:05:24.699 --> 00:05:25.300
Eight of us.

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:27.139
Four generations under one roof.

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:28.399
Mom,

00:05:28.480 --> 00:05:29.439
You just keep spoiling her.

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:30.959
Here we go, here we go.

00:05:31.060 --> 00:05:31.540
Plenty to go around.

00:05:31.540 --> 00:05:34.160
Now this is a real family reunion!

00:05:34.220 --> 00:05:34.579
Mom.

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:36.899
Fanyan,

00:05:37.459 --> 00:05:39.040
This year's Mid-Autumn Festival,

00:05:39.420 --> 00:05:41.139
You make sure to do it right.

00:05:42.019 --> 00:05:42.480
Don't worry.

00:05:43.300 --> 00:05:45.019
I'll definitely win back the face

00:05:45.199 --> 00:05:45.860
We lost in the village.

00:05:45.899 --> 00:05:46.459
That's enough, enough.

00:05:57.740 --> 00:05:58.060
Here.

00:05:59.300 --> 00:05:59.920
You all eat up.

00:06:08.540 --> 00:06:09.019
Big sis,

00:06:10.220 --> 00:06:11.240
Weren't you going to the Maldives?

00:06:15.019 --> 00:06:15.779
Could I even go?

00:06:19.579 --> 00:06:21.220
Could I even go?

00:06:24.319 --> 00:06:26.860
I didn't stop you, Auntie.

00:06:30.379 --> 00:06:31.639
Sis, your husband and Dandan,

00:06:31.639 --> 00:06:32.420
Didn't come back with you?

00:06:37.519 --> 00:06:38.060
This is so spicy.

00:06:38.860 --> 00:06:39.740
Eat slowly.

00:06:43.860 --> 00:06:44.699
That's not important.

00:06:44.980 --> 00:06:45.680
This time we came

00:06:46.199 --> 00:06:47.379
To talk about Xiaofang, right?

00:06:57.560 --> 00:06:58.060
Xiaofang.

00:06:59.019 --> 00:07:00.480
How can you act like nothing happened?

00:07:00.980 --> 00:07:02.240
Because nothing's wrong with me.

00:07:02.699 --> 00:07:03.939
You call this nothing?

00:07:05.079 --> 00:07:05.699
The whole family

00:07:05.939 --> 00:07:07.180
Is worried sick over you.

00:07:07.220 --> 00:07:08.500
How can you be so heartless?

00:07:08.699 --> 00:07:10.019
The baby's inside me,

00:07:10.199 --> 00:07:11.480
And Qi Xiaowei's right there.

00:07:11.800 --> 00:07:13.259
Do you have to act like the sky's falling?

00:07:13.480 --> 00:07:15.019
Let's just eat. Smells great.

00:07:15.019 --> 00:07:15.879
Xiaofang.

00:07:16.379 --> 00:07:17.259
The Qi family

00:07:17.579 --> 00:07:19.480
Practically went back on their word today.

00:07:19.980 --> 00:07:20.699
If they refuse to own up,

00:07:21.139 --> 00:07:22.079
What are you gonna do?

00:07:23.079 --> 00:07:24.019
Today, up on the mountain...

00:07:24.439 --> 00:07:25.720
I, Yang Xiaofang, am pregnant.

00:07:25.860 --> 00:07:26.779
Is that shameful?

00:07:27.699 --> 00:07:28.800
You tell me, is it?

00:07:30.300 --> 00:07:31.420
I think

00:07:34.519 --> 00:07:35.199
It's not shameful.

00:07:36.139 --> 00:07:37.839
Stop with your "I think, I think."

00:07:38.339 --> 00:07:39.339
What you think doesn't matter.

00:07:39.500 --> 00:07:40.639
It's what others think.

00:07:41.120 --> 00:07:41.959
Everyone else thinks

00:07:43.480 --> 00:07:44.100
You're loose.

00:07:44.759 --> 00:07:46.420
What matters is how they see you.

00:07:46.420 --> 00:07:47.180
Your lipstick's smudged.

00:07:47.420 --> 00:07:47.939
Wipe it off.

00:07:49.079 --> 00:07:50.860
I'm not even wearing lipstick!

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:54.839
Fine, I won't say anything. Happy?

00:07:56.480 --> 00:07:57.519
I shouldn't have come back at all.

00:07:57.860 --> 00:07:59.079
Meddling in all your mess.

00:08:01.459 --> 00:08:02.959
You came back to see your mom.

00:08:03.899 --> 00:08:05.060
Was that pointless or not?

00:08:06.699 --> 00:08:08.160
No, no, it wasn't.

00:08:11.180 --> 00:08:11.959
From now on,

00:08:12.519 --> 00:08:14.959
Don't ruin the mood at the table.

00:08:15.759 --> 00:08:17.040
Same rule as always.

00:08:17.740 --> 00:08:19.339
If you've got something to argue about,

00:08:19.959 --> 00:08:21.800
Argue after we've eaten.

00:08:21.959 --> 00:08:25.139
Nothing's more important than eating.

00:08:25.480 --> 00:08:25.800
Come on.

00:08:26.339 --> 00:08:27.019
Mom's right.

00:08:27.019 --> 00:08:28.579
It's not easy for us all to get together.

00:08:28.579 --> 00:08:29.100
Right?

00:08:29.139 --> 00:08:30.220
Thanks for your hard work. Cheers.

00:08:30.220 --> 00:08:30.839
Thanks, thanks, brother.

00:08:30.839 --> 00:08:31.480
Thanks for your hard work, brother.

00:08:31.480 --> 00:08:31.939
Thanks, brother.

00:08:32.500 --> 00:08:33.759
I also chilled a watermelon.

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:34.799
Let me go get it.

00:08:36.580 --> 00:08:37.080
Xiaofang.

00:08:37.840 --> 00:08:40.059
These are the tofu balls you love.

00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:42.519
Your dad bought them first thing this morning.

00:08:44.840 --> 00:08:45.820
Nice, really cold.

00:08:46.259 --> 00:08:47.480
It's all cracked open.

00:08:47.700 --> 00:08:48.600
Come on, come on, dig in.

00:08:49.379 --> 00:08:50.600
Eat, eat, eat.

00:08:53.179 --> 00:08:54.039
Time to eat.

00:08:58.200 --> 00:08:58.700
Alright.

00:09:00.220 --> 00:09:00.879
Xiaowei.

00:09:01.779 --> 00:09:03.019
Xiaowei, come down and eat.

00:09:04.360 --> 00:09:05.100
You silly boy.

00:09:05.139 --> 00:09:05.960
Whatever's going on,

00:09:05.980 --> 00:09:07.419
You gotta finish eating first.

00:09:07.700 --> 00:09:08.200
Come down now.

00:09:08.519 --> 00:09:09.519
Why are you calling him?

00:09:10.279 --> 00:09:11.080
Eat or don't, his choice.

00:09:11.539 --> 00:09:12.279
You're spoiling him rotten.

00:09:25.519 --> 00:09:26.679
You only know how to bully Xiaowei.

00:09:26.919 --> 00:09:28.179
Look at the Yang family across the way.

00:09:28.620 --> 00:09:30.240
A whole bunch of troublemakers are back.

00:09:30.740 --> 00:09:32.539
Today they came to our door.

00:09:32.639 --> 00:09:33.340
Tomorrow, who knows

00:09:33.360 --> 00:09:34.159
What kind of trouble they'll stir up.

00:09:35.039 --> 00:09:36.279
Things are gonna get lively now.

00:09:36.659 --> 00:09:37.340
With Xiaofang shouting like that

00:09:37.340 --> 00:09:38.279
Up on the mountain,

00:09:39.200 --> 00:09:40.720
Xiaowei's now a celebrity in our village.

00:09:41.159 --> 00:09:41.840
So embarrassing.

00:09:41.840 --> 00:09:42.639
My classmates are all saying

00:09:42.639 --> 00:09:44.159
My uncle got someone pregnant unmarried.

00:09:45.539 --> 00:09:46.940
Yang Fanhu's already done time once.

00:09:47.360 --> 00:09:48.720
Does he want to go in a second time?

00:09:49.399 --> 00:09:49.980
Let him make a fuss.

00:09:50.259 --> 00:09:51.259
Let's see how far he takes it.

00:09:51.840 --> 00:09:52.980
Fuss, fuss, fuss!

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:54.840
If this keeps up, how can I marry Xiaofang?

00:09:55.360 --> 00:09:56.899
Why are you rushing to get married?

00:09:57.539 --> 00:09:58.940
Being pregnant before marriage is a good thing.

00:10:00.159 --> 00:10:01.379
The baby's in Yang Xiaofang's belly.

00:10:01.500 --> 00:10:02.179
The ones who should be worried

00:10:02.480 --> 00:10:03.360
Are the Yangs.

00:10:03.679 --> 00:10:04.740
Then am I even a man?

00:10:05.580 --> 00:10:06.340
I want to marry Xiaofang.

00:10:06.639 --> 00:10:07.679
And I need to give her a bride price.

00:10:08.220 --> 00:10:08.899
Bride price?

00:10:09.440 --> 00:10:10.580
Do you know how much it costs

00:10:10.580 --> 00:10:11.419
To marry a wife these days?

00:10:11.779 --> 00:10:12.779
How much could it possibly cost?

00:10:13.519 --> 00:10:14.440
You don't know anything

00:10:14.440 --> 00:10:15.820
Yet you dared to get a girl pregnant.

00:10:17.580 --> 00:10:18.820
Getting a wife these days,

00:10:18.820 --> 00:10:19.980
There's no telling how much it takes.

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:21.600
You need a car and a house.

00:10:21.940 --> 00:10:23.580
Not like when your brother and I married.

00:10:23.919 --> 00:10:25.100
If I'd known, I would've married later.

00:10:25.600 --> 00:10:26.879
Enough.

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:28.100
Have I shortchanged you?

00:10:28.279 --> 00:10:28.639
So what,

00:10:28.639 --> 00:10:30.039
You won't chip in a single cent?

00:10:31.460 --> 00:10:32.659
I mean, when my brother got married,

00:10:32.659 --> 00:10:34.299
You bought him a house and a car.

00:10:34.480 --> 00:10:36.100
You forked over the cash so willingly then.

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:37.860
Why is it so hard when it comes to me?

00:10:38.279 --> 00:10:39.419
I'm asking for money for the sake of

00:10:39.419 --> 00:10:41.039
My future life with Xiaofang.

00:10:41.179 --> 00:10:42.340
What's wrong with supporting me a bit?

00:10:43.120 --> 00:10:43.720
This cured meat

00:10:44.299 --> 00:10:45.360
Was sent by your brother.

00:10:45.799 --> 00:10:46.679
The house renovation

00:10:46.940 --> 00:10:48.080
Was paid for by your brother.

00:10:48.940 --> 00:10:49.860
When your brother married his wife,

00:10:50.299 --> 00:10:51.440
You know what her family does?

00:10:52.039 --> 00:10:52.899
They're contractors, aren't they?

00:10:53.559 --> 00:10:54.279
Contractors.

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:56.559
Your brother's house in the county

00:10:56.580 --> 00:10:57.480
Was bought at insider price.

00:10:57.600 --> 00:10:58.879
Do you know how much he saved?

00:10:59.720 --> 00:11:01.259
He works construction with her dad.

00:11:01.299 --> 00:11:02.480
Do you know how much he makes?

00:11:03.080 --> 00:11:04.059
The little bit you earn,

00:11:04.059 --> 00:11:04.940
No matter how much money I give you,

00:11:04.940 --> 00:11:06.399
It won't be enough after you're married.

00:11:07.580 --> 00:11:08.480
And you complain that I haven't lost

00:11:08.519 --> 00:11:09.600
Enough money on you already?

00:11:11.879 --> 00:11:13.019
Fine, I'm a money-loser.

00:11:14.240 --> 00:11:15.679
If I can't get married, just say so.

00:11:28.899 --> 00:11:29.700
Son

00:11:29.980 --> 00:11:31.080
Don't get worked up

00:11:31.820 --> 00:11:33.659
Xiaofang's belly is huge now

00:11:34.019 --> 00:11:35.340
Who else would take her?

00:11:36.360 --> 00:11:37.039
Right now

00:11:37.220 --> 00:11:38.700
They're begging us

00:11:39.159 --> 00:11:40.159
Not the other way around

00:11:41.539 --> 00:11:42.980
No, how can I not worry?

00:11:43.240 --> 00:11:45.039
The baby's about to be born

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:45.980
And you two, every single day

00:11:45.980 --> 00:11:47.700
It's money, money, money

00:11:48.519 --> 00:11:49.299
What's that supposed to mean?

00:11:51.100 --> 00:11:51.919
Shut your mouth

00:11:53.480 --> 00:11:55.679
You can't even feed yourself

00:11:56.340 --> 00:11:56.799
Getting a wife

00:11:57.039 --> 00:11:58.159
I've gotta pay for it, right?

00:11:58.480 --> 00:12:00.220
I've gotta raise your kid too, right?

00:12:00.480 --> 00:12:02.559
Shut up and let me handle this

00:12:03.080 --> 00:12:03.899
It's a losing deal

00:12:04.159 --> 00:12:04.740
Just drag it out

00:12:05.080 --> 00:12:05.919
The longer we stall

00:12:06.440 --> 00:12:07.039
The cheaper it gets

00:12:08.919 --> 00:12:10.419
It's not Yang Xiaofang you look down on

00:12:10.860 --> 00:12:11.899
It's me you look down on, you...

00:12:12.820 --> 00:12:13.940
What kind of attitude is that?

00:12:14.139 --> 00:12:15.159
Like I owe you something

00:12:16.419 --> 00:12:17.659
Useless piece of trash

00:12:22.539 --> 00:12:23.840
Xiaofang's really got some nerve

00:12:24.240 --> 00:12:25.639
Pregnant before marriage

00:12:25.960 --> 00:12:26.940
And not even hiding it

00:12:27.200 --> 00:12:28.100
Shouting it all over the hills

00:12:28.240 --> 00:12:29.340
When did she and the Qi's second son

00:12:29.360 --> 00:12:30.340
Even hook up?

00:12:30.600 --> 00:12:31.500
And so fast, she already

00:12:31.500 --> 00:12:32.340
Got knocked up

00:12:32.340 --> 00:12:33.519
I saw it with my own eyes today

00:12:33.720 --> 00:12:35.600
The whole Yang family came back

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:36.820
And cornered that kid

00:12:37.100 --> 00:12:38.740
On the field ridge, beat him good

00:12:38.879 --> 00:12:40.139
Even yanked his pants down

00:12:42.399 --> 00:12:43.200
Isn't that Qi Xiaowei?

00:12:44.279 --> 00:12:45.700
Xiaowei, congratulations!

00:12:46.100 --> 00:12:46.980
You're gonna be a dad!

00:12:47.700 --> 00:12:48.340
Xiaowei

00:12:48.600 --> 00:12:50.539
Auntie watched you kids grow up

00:12:50.840 --> 00:12:52.639
You two fell in love freely

00:12:52.799 --> 00:12:54.980
Pregnant before marriage isn't shameful.

00:12:57.000 --> 00:12:57.700
Shameful, my ass!

00:12:58.919 --> 00:13:00.480
Hey, why are you cussing at me?

00:13:00.480 --> 00:13:01.279
He's young

00:13:02.059 --> 00:13:02.940
Thin-skinned

00:13:02.940 --> 00:13:03.799
Poor kid

00:13:03.799 --> 00:13:05.480
Come on, what a thing to say

00:13:05.580 --> 00:13:06.419
Isn't Xiaofang also

00:13:06.419 --> 00:13:07.200
Being totally upfront about it?

00:13:08.059 --> 00:13:08.500
Yeah

00:13:10.940 --> 00:13:13.360
Why didn't you protect yourself?

00:13:13.779 --> 00:13:14.740
What a mess

00:13:17.100 --> 00:13:18.480
Auntie

00:13:18.519 --> 00:13:20.659
Don't be mad anymore

00:13:20.879 --> 00:13:21.940
What's the use of me being mad?

00:13:22.240 --> 00:13:23.200
You're already pregnant

00:13:25.299 --> 00:13:26.779
Of all the guys you could've fallen for

00:13:27.299 --> 00:13:29.100
You had to pick Qi Xiaowei next door

00:13:29.480 --> 00:13:30.720
What's so great about him?

00:13:32.200 --> 00:13:34.000
Xiaowei's got tons of good qualities

00:13:34.279 --> 00:13:35.259
Just take the most superficial one

00:13:35.259 --> 00:13:36.080
He's handsome

00:13:38.539 --> 00:13:39.679
Can a pretty face

00:13:39.860 --> 00:13:41.039
Put rice on the table?

00:13:42.259 --> 00:13:43.519
But it's easy on the eyes!

00:13:44.159 --> 00:13:45.580
And he paints really well too

00:13:45.600 --> 00:13:47.120
So much artistic flair

00:13:47.360 --> 00:13:49.419
An artist wearing cartoon underwear?

00:13:49.759 --> 00:13:50.919
Of all the things to notice

00:13:50.960 --> 00:13:52.080
You had to look at his underwear?

00:13:52.860 --> 00:13:54.100
You're the one who pulled them down

00:13:54.679 --> 00:13:55.220
Anyway

00:13:55.419 --> 00:13:57.159
None of that matters

00:13:58.500 --> 00:13:59.379
What matters is

00:14:01.980 --> 00:14:03.039
He crossed his eyes at me

00:14:10.940 --> 00:14:11.419
Yang Xiaofang.

00:14:11.860 --> 00:14:12.600
Where's your brain?

00:14:14.159 --> 00:14:15.639
Look, everyone else draws them cute.

00:14:15.919 --> 00:14:17.440
Only yours are weird as hell.

00:14:17.679 --> 00:14:19.299
Sure, mine may look weird,

00:14:19.480 --> 00:14:20.720
But they're cute in their own way.

00:14:21.299 --> 00:14:22.039
What I mean is,

00:14:22.039 --> 00:14:23.720
Draw normally like the others,

00:14:24.159 --> 00:14:25.419
Not these eye-rolling,

00:14:25.419 --> 00:14:26.159
Cross-eyed things.

00:14:26.840 --> 00:14:28.179
Boss, didn't you tell us

00:14:28.179 --> 00:14:29.299
When designing the dolls,

00:14:29.299 --> 00:14:31.039
We should be creative?

00:14:31.080 --> 00:14:32.519
Look how creative, how unique!

00:14:32.620 --> 00:14:33.379
I was just bluffing.

00:14:34.159 --> 00:14:34.539
No, wait,

00:14:35.360 --> 00:14:37.440
I was painting a vision for our factory.

00:14:37.980 --> 00:14:39.559
The result of your "uniqueness"

00:14:39.639 --> 00:14:41.720
Is you're always dead last in sales.

00:14:42.200 --> 00:14:43.600
Come on, boss.

00:14:44.120 --> 00:14:45.899
Just wait a little longer.

00:14:46.100 --> 00:14:47.340
I've been reading magazines,

00:14:47.340 --> 00:14:49.279
And the "ugly-cute" style will trend soon.

00:14:49.480 --> 00:14:51.159
Then you'll be raking in the cash.

00:14:52.019 --> 00:14:53.379
Now you're selling me pipe dreams?

00:14:54.200 --> 00:14:54.740
Yang Xiaofang,

00:14:55.200 --> 00:14:56.100
You... why did you come out to work?

00:14:56.100 --> 00:14:56.799
What's the real reason?

00:14:57.059 --> 00:14:58.799
I want to broaden my horizons.

00:14:59.019 --> 00:15:00.360
And once you've broadened them?

00:15:01.279 --> 00:15:02.200
I haven't figured it out yet.

00:15:02.279 --> 00:15:02.600
You...

00:15:04.240 --> 00:15:05.799
You just hug your ugly dolls,

00:15:05.799 --> 00:15:06.519
And take your time thinking.

00:15:09.399 --> 00:15:10.019
They're not ugly!

00:15:40.639 --> 00:15:41.980
Lots of people say I'm weird

00:15:41.980 --> 00:15:43.200
But he never does

00:15:45.100 --> 00:15:46.019
He thinks

00:15:46.980 --> 00:15:48.139
I'm perfect just the way I am

00:15:50.299 --> 00:15:52.240
He says I don't need to change a thing

00:15:53.100 --> 00:15:53.559
Look

00:15:53.960 --> 00:15:54.399
Look, quick

00:15:55.259 --> 00:15:56.139
See that?

00:15:57.399 --> 00:15:59.240
It's as handsome as I am

00:16:01.139 --> 00:16:02.980
Ignore them, they don't get you

00:16:03.039 --> 00:16:04.220
So they don't, but you do?

00:16:04.539 --> 00:16:04.879
I do

00:16:05.519 --> 00:16:06.480
I'm different from them

00:16:07.139 --> 00:16:08.100
I just love you

00:16:08.360 --> 00:16:09.940
Weird and adorable

00:16:10.320 --> 00:16:12.100
What? I didn't catch that

00:16:13.559 --> 00:16:16.240
I just love Yang Xiaofang's

00:16:16.259 --> 00:16:17.899
Adorable weirdness

00:16:17.899 --> 00:16:19.019
Okay, stop it

00:16:19.039 --> 00:16:21.620
I'm Yang Xiaofang's number one fan

00:16:21.720 --> 00:16:22.700
So, my dear fan

00:16:22.700 --> 00:16:24.759
Want an autograph from this superstar?

00:16:24.899 --> 00:16:25.740
Yes, absolutely

00:16:26.639 --> 00:16:27.399
So beautiful

00:16:27.460 --> 00:16:28.379
Who painted all these?

00:16:28.820 --> 00:16:30.019
Foreign artists

00:16:37.659 --> 00:16:38.100
Xiaofang

00:16:39.399 --> 00:16:41.480
To me, you're the most special person

00:16:42.879 --> 00:16:44.019
You never have to change

00:16:44.480 --> 00:16:45.759
I'll always support you

00:16:46.740 --> 00:16:47.679
Just be yourself

00:16:57.460 --> 00:16:57.919
So

00:16:58.600 --> 00:16:59.960
Doesn't he really get me?

00:17:01.799 --> 00:17:03.879
He says you made the first move

00:17:04.279 --> 00:17:05.400
That you seduced him

00:17:06.119 --> 00:17:07.559
Xiaowei said I seduced him?

00:17:07.839 --> 00:17:08.180
Yes

00:17:09.359 --> 00:17:10.400
That's exactly what he said

00:17:11.660 --> 00:17:13.119
I don't believe Xiaowei would say that

00:17:16.059 --> 00:17:17.059
But

00:17:17.579 --> 00:17:21.000
Even if he really did say it

00:17:21.359 --> 00:17:22.460
So what if he did?

00:17:26.180 --> 00:17:27.460
Stop being coy

00:17:27.599 --> 00:17:28.700
So what if he did?

00:17:32.319 --> 00:17:32.640
Come on

00:17:35.759 --> 00:17:37.319
If he really said that

00:17:38.519 --> 00:17:39.460
Then he's not wrong

00:17:40.319 --> 00:17:41.279
I did seduce him

00:17:46.019 --> 00:17:47.079
Come here, come here

00:17:48.559 --> 00:17:49.519
It's nothing, nothing at all

00:17:49.720 --> 00:17:50.660
I'm here, there's nothing

00:17:50.660 --> 00:17:51.299
Are we there yet?

00:17:51.299 --> 00:17:52.440
You're being so mysterious

00:17:52.640 --> 00:17:53.500
Almost there

00:17:54.599 --> 00:17:55.519
Okay, here we are

00:17:55.880 --> 00:17:56.319
We're here

00:17:57.700 --> 00:17:57.960
Open your eyes

00:18:02.680 --> 00:18:04.000
So beautiful

00:18:04.700 --> 00:18:05.140
What do you think?

00:18:05.460 --> 00:18:07.079
You were my inspiration

00:18:08.279 --> 00:18:09.759
Xiaowei, you're a real artist

00:18:11.220 --> 00:18:12.299
When you first started chasing me

00:18:12.299 --> 00:18:14.380
I thought you were bragging to fool me.

00:18:15.119 --> 00:18:16.180
I'd never lie to you

00:18:17.359 --> 00:18:18.180
Xiaofang

00:18:18.940 --> 00:18:20.039
Let's get married

00:18:21.519 --> 00:18:23.259
This isn't just your birthday gift

00:18:23.799 --> 00:18:25.059
It's also a proposal gift

00:18:34.079 --> 00:18:34.460
Here

00:18:38.099 --> 00:18:38.799
This is so spicy

00:18:45.920 --> 00:18:46.279
Come on

00:18:46.880 --> 00:18:47.400
Blow on it

00:18:48.539 --> 00:18:49.440
Blow on it and it won't be spicy

00:19:18.680 --> 00:19:19.200
Xiaowei

00:19:19.200 --> 00:19:20.740
Will you paint a picture for me too?

00:19:44.480 --> 00:19:45.319
Like this?

00:19:58.480 --> 00:19:59.700
Your left hand, move it...

00:20:00.059 --> 00:20:01.480
...up a little more.

00:20:06.680 --> 00:20:08.359
And your right hand, you can...

00:20:08.940 --> 00:20:10.240
...cover your face with it.

00:20:22.660 --> 00:20:24.039
Am I making you nervous?

00:20:25.099 --> 00:20:25.500
No.

00:20:54.319 --> 00:20:54.920
Xiaofang

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:56.700
I love you

00:21:15.799 --> 00:21:16.240
Stop.

00:21:17.980 --> 00:21:18.740
What happened next,

00:21:19.119 --> 00:21:20.279
No need for details.

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:23.039
Wasn't it so romantic?

00:21:23.480 --> 00:21:26.099
So after you two kissed,

00:21:26.960 --> 00:21:28.019
Did you or didn't you?

00:21:28.980 --> 00:21:30.720
Hey, act like an aunt,

00:21:30.720 --> 00:21:31.240
Would you?

00:21:31.680 --> 00:21:33.099
Gossiping about the kids now.

00:21:33.880 --> 00:21:34.579
Well, what came next,

00:21:34.859 --> 00:21:35.579
You know better than her.

00:21:36.759 --> 00:21:38.460
Miss Know-It-All's at it again.

00:21:40.039 --> 00:21:40.559
Xiaofang,

00:21:41.000 --> 00:21:41.920
You didn't know this, did you?

00:21:42.400 --> 00:21:44.500
When your aunt was pregnant with Jingjing,

00:21:44.579 --> 00:21:45.680
She wasn't married either.

00:21:46.700 --> 00:21:47.660
Yang Fanmei!

00:21:48.019 --> 00:21:49.299
What are you butting in for?

00:21:50.039 --> 00:21:51.579
I'm just telling the truth.

00:21:51.579 --> 00:21:52.519
What's wrong with you?

00:21:54.400 --> 00:21:56.000
Back then, Yin Zhiqiang didn't want to marry either.

00:21:56.279 --> 00:21:58.039
But your aunt played her cards

00:21:58.539 --> 00:21:59.700
Way smarter than

00:21:59.920 --> 00:22:00.720
A silly girl like you.

00:22:01.779 --> 00:22:02.839
Go take a hike, will you?

00:22:03.400 --> 00:22:05.200
Don't need you stirring the pot here.

00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:06.140
Tell me more, go on.

00:22:06.180 --> 00:22:07.720
Let me get in on the excitement too!

00:22:10.660 --> 00:22:11.099
Xiaofang,

00:22:12.019 --> 00:22:13.700
Here's how it went.

00:22:15.440 --> 00:22:17.220
I was just like you,

00:22:18.359 --> 00:22:19.579
Back then I was also

00:22:19.980 --> 00:22:22.579
A confused girl pregnant before marriage.

00:22:46.400 --> 00:22:48.000
You owe me an explanation!

00:22:50.079 --> 00:22:50.960
Okay, okay, okay.

00:22:50.960 --> 00:22:51.700
Drinking? Really?

00:22:51.700 --> 00:22:52.700
Do you even know what you're drinking?

00:22:59.680 --> 00:23:00.799
It's water!

00:23:01.980 --> 00:23:02.740
Yang Fanyan!

00:23:02.880 --> 00:23:03.700
Obviously!

00:23:04.599 --> 00:23:05.559
I'm pregnant!

00:23:06.220 --> 00:23:06.599
You...

00:23:07.119 --> 00:23:07.819
Explain yourself.

00:23:08.119 --> 00:23:10.240
My mom won't agree to it.

00:23:10.240 --> 00:23:12.099
So what am I supposed to do?

00:23:12.599 --> 00:23:13.740
I'll tell you what to do.

00:23:15.599 --> 00:23:17.299
Rather than letting the village laugh...

00:23:18.079 --> 00:23:18.839
You think I won't?

00:23:19.779 --> 00:23:20.880
I'll stab myself right now!

00:23:21.099 --> 00:23:22.440
What are you doing?!

00:23:22.440 --> 00:23:22.980
You... you...

00:23:28.900 --> 00:23:29.259
Let go!

00:23:29.859 --> 00:23:30.400
I won't!

00:23:30.779 --> 00:23:31.539
Let go!

00:23:31.559 --> 00:23:32.380
I won't!

00:23:33.799 --> 00:23:34.619
Let go!

00:23:38.619 --> 00:23:39.799
What is this? You think it's funny?

00:23:39.799 --> 00:23:40.539
Go ahead, stab again!

00:23:43.460 --> 00:23:45.039
Where did you get this stuff?

00:23:45.039 --> 00:23:47.200
I can't believe myself.

00:23:47.599 --> 00:23:48.799
Yin Zhiqiang, I'm telling you.

00:23:48.960 --> 00:23:49.819
This time it's fake.

00:23:49.859 --> 00:23:50.920
Next time it'll be real.

00:23:51.400 --> 00:23:52.279
This child is yours.

00:23:52.279 --> 00:23:52.980
You have to marry me.

00:23:53.480 --> 00:23:54.819
Or it's two lives lost, me and the baby.

00:24:10.500 --> 00:24:11.400
Zhiqiang

00:24:13.799 --> 00:24:15.220
Just marry me already

00:24:16.200 --> 00:24:17.099
Zhiqiang

00:24:17.960 --> 00:24:19.200
Zhiqiang

00:24:26.779 --> 00:24:28.720
That's what your aunt did

00:24:29.579 --> 00:24:31.099
Used both carrots and sticks

00:24:31.359 --> 00:24:32.539
You think I wanted to?

00:24:33.500 --> 00:24:34.039
Xiaofang

00:24:34.960 --> 00:24:36.220
I think a woman's biggest mistake

00:24:36.859 --> 00:24:38.859
Is picking the wrong man

00:24:39.420 --> 00:24:40.299
And making it worse

00:24:40.579 --> 00:24:41.720
By getting pregnant

00:24:42.420 --> 00:24:43.619
You have no idea back then

00:24:43.660 --> 00:24:44.579
In the village

00:24:44.859 --> 00:24:46.220
People pointed fingers at me

00:24:46.240 --> 00:24:47.440
Saying all kinds of things

00:24:48.000 --> 00:24:49.539
I only had one option

00:24:49.799 --> 00:24:50.700
Get married

00:24:51.799 --> 00:24:53.380
After Jingjing was born

00:24:53.799 --> 00:24:55.460
I had to leave her with her grandma

00:24:56.359 --> 00:24:57.460
That's why to this day

00:24:57.460 --> 00:24:58.420
Jingjing isn't close to me

00:24:58.720 --> 00:25:00.180
But I was so young back then

00:25:00.619 --> 00:25:01.339
With no stable job

00:25:01.339 --> 00:25:02.680
What could I do?

00:25:02.799 --> 00:25:04.200
How could I raise a child?

00:25:06.420 --> 00:25:07.079
I really regret it

00:25:07.259 --> 00:25:08.559
I should've told you sooner

00:25:08.559 --> 00:25:09.220
About my story

00:25:09.400 --> 00:25:10.420
So you could

00:25:11.160 --> 00:25:12.339
Use it as a cautionary tale

00:25:13.660 --> 00:25:14.519
Now look at this

00:25:15.380 --> 00:25:16.619
You're repeating the same mistake

00:25:17.279 --> 00:25:17.779
Auntie

00:25:20.000 --> 00:25:21.019
I don't think you were wrong

00:25:22.000 --> 00:25:22.779
Slow down, slow down

00:25:22.940 --> 00:25:23.859
Don't strain the baby

00:25:28.480 --> 00:25:30.000
Maybe you were just a bit unlucky

00:25:30.380 --> 00:25:31.099
Unlucky how?

00:25:32.059 --> 00:25:32.720
Bet on the wrong man

00:25:34.640 --> 00:25:35.960
You clearly knew

00:25:35.960 --> 00:25:37.880
Uncle Zhiqiang didn't want to marry

00:25:37.900 --> 00:25:38.720
But you forced him into it

00:25:39.079 --> 00:25:40.539
If the foundation isn't solid

00:25:40.779 --> 00:25:41.720
The house is bound to fall

00:25:42.059 --> 00:25:43.960
If the marriage wasn't willing

00:25:44.220 --> 00:25:45.180
It was bound to fall apart

00:25:45.400 --> 00:25:46.079
Am I right?

00:25:49.339 --> 00:25:50.460
Yeah

00:25:53.559 --> 00:25:54.740
You were also short on courage

00:25:55.700 --> 00:25:56.960
You worried about what others

00:25:56.960 --> 00:25:58.019
Would gossip about

00:25:58.119 --> 00:25:59.859
You felt you couldn't stay in the village

00:25:59.859 --> 00:26:00.819
So you had to go to the city

00:26:01.200 --> 00:26:01.799
Then you worried

00:26:01.799 --> 00:26:03.000
You couldn't raise Jingjing well

00:26:03.039 --> 00:26:04.299
So you handed her to the elders

00:26:05.140 --> 00:26:06.180
It looks like

00:26:06.180 --> 00:26:08.079
You were making smart choices

00:26:08.339 --> 00:26:10.019
But really, you were running away

00:26:10.019 --> 00:26:11.000
You never faced

00:26:11.000 --> 00:26:11.819
The problem head-on

00:26:12.140 --> 00:26:12.880
Right, Auntie?

00:26:13.900 --> 00:26:14.779
Seems like you have a point

00:26:15.299 --> 00:26:15.900
I swear, you're

00:26:16.460 --> 00:26:17.640
Such a chameleon

00:26:23.700 --> 00:26:24.339
Auntie

00:26:25.460 --> 00:26:26.180
Little Auntie

00:26:26.660 --> 00:26:27.299
As for me

00:26:27.420 --> 00:26:29.220
I'm different from Auntie back then

00:26:29.460 --> 00:26:30.960
Because I have you guys

00:26:31.220 --> 00:26:31.960
I have you all

00:26:32.660 --> 00:26:34.819
So I have both courage and luck

00:26:35.539 --> 00:26:36.519
That's why I'm not afraid of anything

00:26:59.819 --> 00:27:01.180
I brought you guys presents!

00:27:02.259 --> 00:27:03.420
Presents? What kind?

00:27:03.539 --> 00:27:04.200
What is this?

00:27:05.079 --> 00:27:05.700
Which one's mine?

00:27:08.220 --> 00:27:09.299
Deer antlers.

00:27:09.960 --> 00:27:10.819
Horse face.

00:27:11.400 --> 00:27:12.380
Cow's body, I guess.

00:27:12.819 --> 00:27:13.140
And this...

00:27:13.460 --> 00:27:14.140
A donkey's tail.

00:27:15.460 --> 00:27:17.039
Why are its eyes rolled up like that?

00:27:18.019 --> 00:27:18.640
It's a total mishmash.

00:27:19.180 --> 00:27:19.819
Doesn't it look like you?

00:27:21.940 --> 00:27:23.039
I look like a mishmash?

00:27:24.079 --> 00:27:24.940
Are you praising me

00:27:24.960 --> 00:27:25.779
Or insulting me?

00:27:26.079 --> 00:27:26.819
This is a peacock, right?

00:27:27.299 --> 00:27:28.319
Think it looks like you?

00:27:28.440 --> 00:27:29.619
This peacock is just like me.

00:27:29.759 --> 00:27:31.380
At least it's better than a mishmash.

00:27:31.380 --> 00:27:32.460
Looks like anything but yourself.

00:27:32.460 --> 00:27:33.619
You're clearly just a pheasant

00:27:33.720 --> 00:27:34.279
With peacock feathers stuck in.

00:27:34.279 --> 00:27:35.680
How am I a pheasant?

00:27:36.200 --> 00:27:38.700
In Xiaofang's eyes, I'm a peacock.

00:27:38.700 --> 00:27:39.960
Right?

00:27:39.960 --> 00:27:40.720
Show me you can fly then.

00:27:40.759 --> 00:27:41.579
Watch me fly!

00:27:45.339 --> 00:27:45.859
Fanyan.

00:27:46.160 --> 00:27:47.759
Why can't you just understand me a little?

00:27:48.240 --> 00:27:49.019
You're this old already,

00:27:49.240 --> 00:27:50.240
And still so stubborn?

00:28:54.880 --> 00:28:55.440
Hurry up and cut it!

00:28:55.519 --> 00:28:56.660
Before he wakes up!

00:28:59.380 --> 00:29:00.140
Xiaofang!

00:29:01.339 --> 00:29:02.180
Cut it, quick!

00:29:02.539 --> 00:29:03.359
He's gonna wake up soon.

00:29:04.119 --> 00:29:04.880
How am I supposed to cut it?

00:29:05.019 --> 00:29:05.460
Help me out!

00:29:06.200 --> 00:29:06.660
Over here, over here!

00:29:06.660 --> 00:29:07.579
Here, here, here!

00:29:07.859 --> 00:29:08.240
Yes!

00:29:19.640 --> 00:29:20.240
Hey, what are you doing?

00:29:20.359 --> 00:29:20.960
What do you think I'm doing?

00:29:24.559 --> 00:29:25.480
I said I'm not cutting it!

00:29:25.660 --> 00:29:26.700
What are you yelling for?

00:29:27.099 --> 00:29:28.240
You're getting married, becoming a dad!

00:29:28.599 --> 00:29:29.740
You don't listen to me anymore, huh?

00:29:30.099 --> 00:29:32.000
Getting married and shaving my head

00:29:32.119 --> 00:29:32.960
Are two different things!

00:29:38.460 --> 00:29:38.819
Dad,

00:29:39.619 --> 00:29:40.460
So you mean

00:29:40.599 --> 00:29:42.640
You agree to let me marry Xiaofang

00:29:42.700 --> 00:29:43.839
And give me the bride price money?

00:29:45.980 --> 00:29:47.339
I say one thing, you say another.

00:29:47.579 --> 00:29:49.099
You're way off the topic!

00:29:54.160 --> 00:29:54.740
What are you trying to do?

00:29:55.180 --> 00:29:55.900
I'll compromise once more.

00:29:56.240 --> 00:29:57.099
You give me that money,

00:29:57.119 --> 00:29:58.180
And I'll shave my head.

00:29:58.259 --> 00:29:58.980
Bull!

00:29:59.319 --> 00:30:00.680
Is your hair made of gold?

00:30:00.680 --> 00:30:01.599
That valuable, huh?

00:30:01.980 --> 00:30:02.619
Shave it or don't.

00:30:02.819 --> 00:30:03.700
See how people will laugh at you.

00:30:04.279 --> 00:30:05.619
All I want is fairness here.

00:30:05.700 --> 00:30:07.039
Just give me what's owed to me.

00:30:07.400 --> 00:30:08.440
Besides, Xiaofang already said

00:30:08.680 --> 00:30:09.839
She's marrying me, not the bride price.

00:30:11.000 --> 00:30:11.339
You...

00:30:11.920 --> 00:30:13.200
You believe what she says?

00:30:13.480 --> 00:30:14.299
If you don't give it to her,

00:30:14.500 --> 00:30:15.579
See if she still marries you!

00:30:16.000 --> 00:30:16.819
You don't understand her.

00:30:17.140 --> 00:30:18.099
Oh, we don't understand, huh?

00:30:18.099 --> 00:30:18.779
And you do?

00:30:19.200 --> 00:30:19.500
Fine.

00:30:20.740 --> 00:30:21.940
Let me show you how well you know her.

00:30:22.660 --> 00:30:23.099
Password.

00:30:24.079 --> 00:30:24.779
That's private!

00:30:25.259 --> 00:30:25.859
Password!

00:30:25.980 --> 00:30:28.400
Password, password, give it!

00:30:28.980 --> 00:30:29.319
Say it!

00:30:29.339 --> 00:30:29.720
Say it!

00:30:32.279 --> 00:30:32.799
1314.

00:30:34.180 --> 00:30:35.180
1314?

00:30:35.220 --> 00:30:35.759
1314.

00:30:37.400 --> 00:30:38.920
So my son's a real romantic.

00:30:38.960 --> 00:30:40.819
Romantic my foot! "Forever and ever"?

00:30:41.079 --> 00:30:42.519
You're ruining your dad forever and ever!

00:30:46.440 --> 00:30:47.420
This is just for engagement.

00:30:47.640 --> 00:30:49.019
For the wedding, it won't be this one.

00:30:49.299 --> 00:30:49.799
For the wedding,

00:30:49.799 --> 00:30:50.720
I'll get a big diamond ring.

00:30:50.880 --> 00:30:52.319
A big diamond ring too?

00:30:53.180 --> 00:30:53.700
Xiaofang,

00:30:54.400 --> 00:30:55.920
Didn't you say you're getting married?

00:30:56.200 --> 00:30:57.059
Have you discussed the bride price?

00:30:57.720 --> 00:30:58.240
Talked about it ages ago.

00:30:59.240 --> 00:30:59.680
Yeah, we talked.

00:31:00.079 --> 00:31:00.559
We talked.

00:31:01.839 --> 00:31:02.240
How much?

00:31:02.859 --> 00:31:03.319
Doesn't matter.

00:31:03.960 --> 00:31:04.920
Doesn't matter?

00:31:05.680 --> 00:31:07.180
How can it not matter?

00:31:07.559 --> 00:31:09.519
In the countryside now, men outnumber women.

00:31:09.519 --> 00:31:11.920
Requirements have doubled since years ago.

00:31:13.579 --> 00:31:15.039
So how much bride price did you get?

00:31:16.319 --> 00:31:16.940
It's a secret.

00:31:18.500 --> 00:31:19.599
Fine, forget it then.

00:31:20.259 --> 00:31:23.259
Xiaofang, I miss you.

00:31:24.519 --> 00:31:27.599
Dad's asking your family's bride price.

00:31:28.539 --> 00:31:29.059
Hehe.

00:31:39.940 --> 00:31:41.880
What are you laughing at?

00:31:42.640 --> 00:31:44.059
He's asking about the bride price.

00:31:44.599 --> 00:31:45.759
Qi Xiaowei's not bad!

00:31:45.940 --> 00:31:47.140
He convinced his dad already?

00:31:49.240 --> 00:31:49.960
Reply for me.

00:31:50.380 --> 00:31:51.359
My hands are covered in herbs.

00:31:51.579 --> 00:31:52.160
Just tell him,

00:31:52.559 --> 00:31:53.420
Whatever bride price is fine.

00:31:53.460 --> 00:31:54.079
I don't care.

00:31:54.259 --> 00:31:55.900
Don't care, don't care...

00:31:55.920 --> 00:31:56.920
Wait, Xiaofang.

00:31:57.160 --> 00:31:58.059
This kind of thing,

00:31:58.059 --> 00:31:59.579
How can you not care?

00:31:59.740 --> 00:32:01.140
You can't be careless about this!

00:32:02.960 --> 00:32:05.099
Ask too little and they'll look down on us.

00:32:05.200 --> 00:32:06.740
They'll think you're desperate for him.

00:32:06.740 --> 00:32:07.480
Exactly.

00:32:08.279 --> 00:32:09.559
Let me think how to reply.

00:32:12.819 --> 00:32:15.039
A car and a house.

00:32:18.299 --> 00:32:18.880
Sent.

00:32:19.039 --> 00:32:19.440
Take a look.

00:32:20.740 --> 00:32:21.680
Oh my god.

00:32:22.279 --> 00:32:22.880
What does that mean?

00:32:23.200 --> 00:32:23.819
What does it mean?

00:32:24.059 --> 00:32:25.420
"Moving" means a car.

00:32:25.579 --> 00:32:27.299
"Not moving" means real estate, a house.

00:32:27.420 --> 00:32:29.680
So she wants a house and a car.

00:32:31.599 --> 00:32:32.660
You call this knowing her?

00:32:33.960 --> 00:32:35.400
You call this not caring about bride price?

00:32:36.539 --> 00:32:37.640
But isn't that just how it should be?

00:32:37.920 --> 00:32:38.599
As a man,

00:32:38.599 --> 00:32:39.420
Shouldn't I provide these?

00:32:39.799 --> 00:32:40.420
Besides,

00:32:40.420 --> 00:32:41.940
Xiaofang's not asking for a mansion

00:32:42.160 --> 00:32:42.920
Or a luxury car.

00:32:43.240 --> 00:32:44.519
Look carefully.

00:32:44.559 --> 00:32:46.140
There's also "Shake off the in-laws, help out your family."

00:32:46.680 --> 00:32:48.420
"Shake off" means shake off trouble.

00:32:48.799 --> 00:32:49.740
Start a separate household.

00:32:50.099 --> 00:32:52.200
Absolutely no living with the in-laws.

00:32:52.400 --> 00:32:54.079
Marriage nowadays has so many rules.

00:32:54.240 --> 00:32:55.519
And "help out"

00:32:55.680 --> 00:32:56.740
Means helping her own family.

00:32:56.900 --> 00:32:57.799
The bride price money

00:32:57.839 --> 00:32:58.940
Must stay with her family.

00:32:59.220 --> 00:33:00.039
Holiday and birthday gifts,

00:33:00.140 --> 00:33:01.079
Gifts are a must.

00:33:01.240 --> 00:33:03.220
Isn't bride price discouraged these days?

00:33:03.519 --> 00:33:04.759
Sure, having it is nice,

00:33:04.839 --> 00:33:06.619
But not having it isn't the end of the world.

00:33:06.680 --> 00:33:07.500
How can that be okay?

00:33:07.859 --> 00:33:08.799
She's not even married in yet,

00:33:08.799 --> 00:33:10.140
And she's already trying to shake us off.

00:33:11.460 --> 00:33:13.099
Just trying to funnel money to her family.

00:33:13.700 --> 00:33:14.740
You and Xiaofang used to be

00:33:14.740 --> 00:33:15.819
Childhood sweethearts, sure.

00:33:16.000 --> 00:33:16.819
But look at now.

00:33:17.599 --> 00:33:19.279
A road separates the two families.

00:33:19.400 --> 00:33:20.680
People have changed long ago.

00:33:21.059 --> 00:33:22.380
And you're still stuck on "one, three, one, four."

00:33:22.380 --> 00:33:23.779
I say you're a total idiot.

00:33:24.599 --> 00:33:25.480
Xiaofang didn't send this.

00:33:25.480 --> 00:33:25.940
I'll go ask her.

00:33:26.119 --> 00:33:26.539
Come back!

00:33:27.079 --> 00:33:27.599
Right now,

00:33:27.880 --> 00:33:28.339
You can't go.

00:33:28.640 --> 00:33:30.160
The tenser it gets, the calmer you stay.

00:33:30.339 --> 00:33:31.380
You idiot!

00:33:31.460 --> 00:33:32.359
What is there to ask?

00:33:32.559 --> 00:33:33.299
Xiaofang is just

00:33:33.299 --> 00:33:34.240
Sweet-talking you.

00:33:34.380 --> 00:33:35.200
Son,

00:33:35.480 --> 00:33:36.660
You've been fooled.

00:33:37.539 --> 00:33:38.960
You've been brainless since childhood.

00:33:39.180 --> 00:33:41.000
How'd you get even worse as an adult?

00:33:41.400 --> 00:33:43.500
You've disgraced the entire Qi family!

00:33:43.799 --> 00:33:44.359
Do you know what you

00:33:44.359 --> 00:33:45.240
Look like right now?

00:33:45.980 --> 00:33:46.819
You look just like

00:33:47.259 --> 00:33:48.819
A bitter woman cheated of money and love.

00:33:48.819 --> 00:33:49.759
A bitter woman, you get it?

00:33:49.759 --> 00:33:50.259
Bitter!

00:33:52.279 --> 00:33:52.660
You...

00:33:55.140 --> 00:33:56.200
Son, you...

00:33:56.319 --> 00:33:57.660
Don't do anything stupid!

00:34:20.639 --> 00:34:21.159
Xiaowei

00:34:22.199 --> 00:34:22.940
Don't run, slow down

00:34:23.280 --> 00:34:25.239
I came as soon as I got your message

00:34:26.119 --> 00:34:26.920
Still, you shouldn't run

00:34:27.039 --> 00:34:28.079
Look how big your belly is

00:34:28.159 --> 00:34:29.159
What if you fall?

00:34:29.780 --> 00:34:30.360
I won't

00:34:30.360 --> 00:34:31.739
I've been running here since I was a kid

00:34:32.960 --> 00:34:33.400
Look

00:34:34.460 --> 00:34:35.400
If you step on this

00:34:35.860 --> 00:34:36.659
You'll definitely fall

00:34:36.980 --> 00:34:38.460
You're going to be a mom

00:34:38.800 --> 00:34:40.099
Can't you act like one?

00:34:40.219 --> 00:34:41.619
I'm not a mom yet, am I?

00:34:41.920 --> 00:34:42.760
What are you doing?

00:34:44.320 --> 00:34:44.679
Wait

00:34:45.840 --> 00:34:46.400
Xiaowei

00:34:48.000 --> 00:34:49.059
You cut your hair

00:34:49.340 --> 00:34:49.960
Let me see

00:34:51.840 --> 00:34:52.599
Let me have a look

00:34:53.360 --> 00:34:54.400
Who cut it for you?

00:34:54.960 --> 00:34:55.659
My dad

00:34:57.699 --> 00:34:59.039
He told you to cut it and you just did?

00:34:59.400 --> 00:35:00.659
You looked so handsome with long hair

00:35:04.519 --> 00:35:05.760
Yang Xiaofang, you've changed

00:35:08.099 --> 00:35:08.760
Now spill it

00:35:09.420 --> 00:35:10.860
That "A car and a house"

00:35:10.860 --> 00:35:11.980
"Shake off the in-laws, help out your family"

00:35:12.019 --> 00:35:12.579
What's that about?

00:35:13.739 --> 00:35:15.260
Those are new terms I just learned today

00:35:15.719 --> 00:35:16.559
Let me tell you, getting married nowadays

00:35:16.559 --> 00:35:17.579
Is really terrifying

00:35:18.119 --> 00:35:19.639
"A car and a house" means

00:35:19.679 --> 00:35:20.860
A house and a car

00:35:20.860 --> 00:35:22.400
And "Shake off the in-laws, help out your family" means

00:35:22.400 --> 00:35:22.719
You have to...

00:35:22.860 --> 00:35:23.860
So you really posted it?

00:35:24.780 --> 00:35:25.860
Of course I didn't post it

00:35:26.019 --> 00:35:27.659
Xiao Zhu and Xiao Chao posted it as a joke

00:35:28.460 --> 00:35:28.699
Wait

00:35:28.699 --> 00:35:30.199
How could you let them mess around like that?

00:35:30.360 --> 00:35:31.920
Now my dad and everyone got the wrong idea

00:35:32.099 --> 00:35:33.280
They think you'll jack up the price.

00:35:34.579 --> 00:35:36.119
What about you? Do you think that?

00:35:36.480 --> 00:35:38.000
Of course that's not what I think

00:35:38.940 --> 00:35:39.539
Then we're fine

00:35:40.159 --> 00:35:40.719
As for the bride price

00:35:40.739 --> 00:35:41.719
Haven't we already discussed it?

00:35:49.199 --> 00:35:49.760
Don't worry.

00:35:50.360 --> 00:35:50.980
About the bride price,

00:35:51.039 --> 00:35:52.440
I'll definitely fight for you all the way.

00:35:53.599 --> 00:35:54.139
You're silly.

00:35:54.579 --> 00:35:55.460
The sun's behind you.

00:35:57.280 --> 00:35:58.079
Right. Here.

00:35:59.880 --> 00:36:01.280
My goose just laid this egg.

00:36:01.400 --> 00:36:02.280
I snuck it out for you.

00:36:02.420 --> 00:36:03.199
When I left the house,

00:36:03.199 --> 00:36:04.300
It followed me the whole way.

00:36:06.280 --> 00:36:07.019
The egg's already been boiled.

00:36:07.039 --> 00:36:07.960
And it still followed you?

00:36:09.440 --> 00:36:10.460
Okay, I may have

00:36:10.460 --> 00:36:11.159
Added a little bit of

00:36:11.320 --> 00:36:12.239
Artistic embellishment.

00:36:12.599 --> 00:36:13.860
But this goose egg is real,

00:36:14.480 --> 00:36:16.300
And my heart for Yang Xiaofang is real too.

00:36:21.420 --> 00:36:23.639
But you look bad with your long hair cut.

00:36:23.940 --> 00:36:25.119
Your face is so round,

00:36:25.500 --> 00:36:26.260
You'll look like a braised egg.

00:36:30.219 --> 00:36:31.519
If he cuts his, I'll grow mine out.

00:36:32.139 --> 00:36:33.400
Just wait. In a year,

00:36:33.519 --> 00:36:34.940
I'll still be that handsome fuzzy-headed guy.

00:36:37.280 --> 00:36:37.840
Well said.

00:36:38.260 --> 00:36:39.460
As long as we don't change,

00:36:39.460 --> 00:36:40.760
Nothing can change us.

00:36:41.920 --> 00:36:42.239
Let's go.

00:36:43.340 --> 00:36:43.780
Braised egg.

00:36:44.679 --> 00:36:45.260
Braised egg.

00:36:45.579 --> 00:36:46.820
Braised egg, braised egg.

00:36:47.480 --> 00:36:48.639
Maybe the villagers

00:36:48.699 --> 00:36:51.019
Don't understand what Xiaowei and I have.

00:36:51.719 --> 00:36:52.820
But actually,

00:36:52.820 --> 00:36:54.139
What they don't know is,

00:36:54.820 --> 00:36:55.500
When I was ten years old...

00:36:55.500 --> 00:36:56.039
Xiaofang.

00:36:56.940 --> 00:36:58.059
That was the year I endured

00:36:58.119 --> 00:36:59.320
The most gossip and rumors.

00:36:59.739 --> 00:37:01.880
Xiaowei was the only one who held my hand.

00:37:02.860 --> 00:37:03.719
I bought you a popsicle.

00:37:04.280 --> 00:37:04.920
I don't want it.

00:37:06.880 --> 00:37:07.940
I've arranged everything.

00:37:08.159 --> 00:37:09.420
I came back this time to take you with me.

00:37:09.719 --> 00:37:10.099
Okay?

00:37:10.360 --> 00:37:10.980
Come with Mommy.

00:37:11.559 --> 00:37:11.880
Let's go.

00:37:12.260 --> 00:37:13.539
No, I don't need you to care about me.

00:37:13.840 --> 00:37:15.280
What are you doing, Xiaofang?

00:37:15.480 --> 00:37:16.699
Your dad's been locked up.

00:37:17.039 --> 00:37:17.619
If I don't take care of you, who will?

00:37:17.619 --> 00:37:18.360
I said, I don't need you to take care of me!

00:37:18.360 --> 00:37:19.159
I don't need you!

00:37:19.539 --> 00:37:21.300
If you leave with him, don't come back!

00:37:21.460 --> 00:37:23.059
Her dad's been locked up, I heard.

00:37:24.300 --> 00:37:25.860
Is that her mom coming to get her?

00:37:26.719 --> 00:37:28.260
How can she treat her mom like that?

00:37:28.340 --> 00:37:29.320
What business is it of yours?

00:37:29.739 --> 00:37:30.659
Mind your own business!

00:37:34.280 --> 00:37:35.260
Xiaofang, let's go.

00:37:39.380 --> 00:37:39.960
Xiaofang!

00:37:41.079 --> 00:37:41.699
Xiaofang!

00:37:43.119 --> 00:37:43.880
Xiaofang!

00:37:53.960 --> 00:37:56.059
The village gossip

00:37:56.079 --> 00:37:57.519
Is like the mountain wind.

00:37:58.340 --> 00:38:01.139
From the east today, smelling of dirt.

00:38:02.119 --> 00:38:04.320
Tomorrow it drifts west and is gone.

00:38:05.519 --> 00:38:07.280
I never care what others say.

00:38:07.880 --> 00:38:09.400
I just want to hold on to what's in my heart,

00:38:09.440 --> 00:38:11.579
This steadiness and sincerity.

00:38:40.400 --> 00:38:41.260
Let me tell you guys

00:38:41.659 --> 00:38:42.880
When Xiaofang and I were kids

00:38:42.880 --> 00:38:43.920
The elders in the village said

00:38:44.519 --> 00:38:46.019
If you catch a firefly

00:38:46.019 --> 00:38:47.159
You get to make a wish

00:38:47.719 --> 00:38:48.980
My biggest wish right now

00:38:49.340 --> 00:38:50.739
Is that my wedding with Xiaofang

00:38:50.900 --> 00:38:51.900
Goes off without a hitch

00:38:52.420 --> 00:38:53.320
I mean, come on

00:38:53.320 --> 00:38:54.619
You said it yourself before

00:38:54.699 --> 00:38:56.760
"I'll never marry or have kids early"

00:38:57.440 --> 00:38:57.860
And look at you

00:38:58.139 --> 00:38:59.400
Out of all of us, you're pretty much

00:38:59.400 --> 00:39:00.440
The first one to make it out there

00:39:00.820 --> 00:39:01.619
Are you really okay

00:39:01.619 --> 00:39:02.719
Getting reeled in by Yang Xiaofang?

00:39:05.539 --> 00:39:06.300
Yeah, I'm good with it

00:39:09.199 --> 00:39:10.519
I came back just to

00:39:10.880 --> 00:39:11.820
Get married, have a kid

00:39:12.000 --> 00:39:12.760
And in a few months

00:39:12.760 --> 00:39:13.420
I'm heading back out

00:39:13.599 --> 00:39:14.179
But

00:39:14.639 --> 00:39:16.739
People in this village are so nosy

00:39:17.099 --> 00:39:17.780
Behind your back

00:39:18.039 --> 00:39:18.940
They're always pointing fingers

00:39:18.940 --> 00:39:20.219
No sense of boundaries at all

00:39:20.480 --> 00:39:21.480
Well, you know how it is

00:39:21.480 --> 00:39:22.320
In a village like ours

00:39:22.579 --> 00:39:23.699
With all the aunties and uncles

00:39:23.699 --> 00:39:25.059
Everyone's related somehow

00:39:25.639 --> 00:39:26.320
That thing you mentioned

00:39:26.320 --> 00:39:27.320
That sense of whatever

00:39:27.320 --> 00:39:28.860
That's a city folk thing

00:39:28.900 --> 00:39:30.059
In our village, that doesn't exist

00:39:30.559 --> 00:39:31.980
Bro, let me be straight with you

00:39:32.800 --> 00:39:33.539
You gotta get Xiaofang

00:39:33.539 --> 00:39:34.500
To change that personality of hers

00:39:34.940 --> 00:39:35.880
What's wrong with Xiaofang's personality?

00:39:37.280 --> 00:39:38.219
Why should she change?

00:39:38.380 --> 00:39:39.139
She's free-spirited

00:39:39.139 --> 00:39:40.059
Does whatever she wants

00:39:40.539 --> 00:39:41.659
That's exactly what I love about her

00:39:42.900 --> 00:39:43.519
So her shouting up on the mountain

00:39:43.519 --> 00:39:44.340
Announcing she's pregnant

00:39:44.340 --> 00:39:45.719
You don't mind that at all?

00:39:46.280 --> 00:39:46.820
Give it a rest

00:39:54.440 --> 00:39:55.539
She's gonna be a mom

00:39:56.619 --> 00:39:57.880
She should be happy, right?

00:40:02.639 --> 00:40:03.599
But honestly

00:40:05.199 --> 00:40:06.159
This whole thing

00:40:06.539 --> 00:40:07.900
Did come a bit too suddenly

00:40:09.159 --> 00:40:10.559
We haven't even dated that long

00:40:11.059 --> 00:40:12.079
And suddenly I'm a dad

00:40:14.860 --> 00:40:15.699
But she's already pregnant

00:40:15.699 --> 00:40:16.980
I've gotta take responsibility, right?

00:40:18.360 --> 00:40:18.699
Oh, by the way

00:40:19.099 --> 00:40:20.440
Doesn't your brother work

00:40:20.719 --> 00:40:22.380
At the county cultural center?

00:40:23.219 --> 00:40:24.800
I wanna hold an art exhibition

00:40:25.199 --> 00:40:25.760
A what now?

00:40:25.920 --> 00:40:26.559
An art exhibition

00:40:26.639 --> 00:40:27.739
Sell paintings, make money

00:40:28.000 --> 00:40:29.159
I gotta support myself

00:40:29.639 --> 00:40:30.539
We've gotta help you out

00:40:31.840 --> 00:40:32.380
That's what bros are for

00:40:33.840 --> 00:40:34.480
Take a look at these

00:40:38.000 --> 00:40:38.719
I painted them all

00:40:39.940 --> 00:40:40.559
They can be sold

00:40:42.179 --> 00:40:43.199
Should've picked up painting myself

00:40:45.119 --> 00:40:46.739
You've done quite a lot here

00:40:47.139 --> 00:40:47.860
Not bad at all

00:40:48.320 --> 00:40:49.619
Looks like you can make good money

00:41:04.280 --> 00:41:04.780
Wait, wait

00:41:06.059 --> 00:41:07.219
Who's this naked one?

00:41:07.800 --> 00:41:08.679
Who is she?

00:41:10.940 --> 00:41:11.639
Xiaofang, obviously

00:41:12.400 --> 00:41:13.280
That's Yang Xiaofang

00:41:13.579 --> 00:41:14.400
Who else could it be?

00:41:14.539 --> 00:41:15.300
Other than her

00:41:15.300 --> 00:41:16.980
Who'd strip down and let you paint them?

00:41:26.239 --> 00:41:27.360
Why did you send it out?

00:41:28.519 --> 00:41:29.780
Stop sharing it! Recall it, now!

00:41:29.780 --> 00:41:30.340
Just sharing, sharing

00:41:47.219 --> 00:41:48.239
Such strong wind

00:42:10.800 --> 00:42:11.800
The wind's picking up.

00:42:14.159 --> 00:42:15.519
Weather's about to turn.

00:42:27.340 --> 00:42:27.719
Xiao Lin!

00:42:28.519 --> 00:42:28.900
Xiao Lin!

00:42:29.679 --> 00:42:30.000
Hurry!

00:42:32.719 --> 00:42:33.400
Who's this?

00:42:33.619 --> 00:42:34.019
Yeah, right?

00:42:35.760 --> 00:42:37.400
Looks like Yang Xiaofang.

00:42:38.360 --> 00:42:39.820
Who'd do something so shameless?

00:42:40.199 --> 00:42:41.940
These young folks sure have guts.

00:42:42.019 --> 00:42:43.000
So wild these days!

00:42:43.260 --> 00:42:44.000
What do you know?

00:42:44.079 --> 00:42:44.719
It's called being open-minded.

00:42:45.860 --> 00:42:46.960
Open-minded, my foot!

00:42:46.960 --> 00:42:48.179
She's stripped bare!

00:42:48.619 --> 00:42:49.659
They're young, you know?

00:42:49.679 --> 00:42:50.500
They live wild.

00:42:51.019 --> 00:42:52.039
What decent girl would

00:42:52.039 --> 00:42:53.280
Strip naked to be painted?

00:42:54.539 --> 00:42:56.099
I don't think Yang Xiaofang

00:42:56.119 --> 00:42:57.159
Can stay in this village anymore.

00:42:57.900 --> 00:42:58.760
How could she do that?

00:43:23.380 --> 00:43:25.320
This is Xiaofang's own business.

00:43:25.679 --> 00:43:26.980
But you bunch of grown-ups

00:43:26.980 --> 00:43:28.099
Had to butt in.

00:43:28.519 --> 00:43:29.960
A perfectly good relationship,

00:43:30.260 --> 00:43:32.219
And you all ruined it.

00:43:32.219 --> 00:43:33.579
Why do I feel like ever since you got back,

00:43:33.579 --> 00:43:34.739
You're like a completely different person?

00:43:35.480 --> 00:43:37.260
This isn't just between you and Qi Xiaowei

00:43:37.340 --> 00:43:38.420
As two people anymore.

00:43:38.679 --> 00:43:41.039
This is now a war between two families.

00:43:41.079 --> 00:43:41.780
What... what are you doing?

00:43:42.940 --> 00:43:43.599
Yang Fanmei!

00:43:43.760 --> 00:43:44.980
You dare throw a shoe at me?

00:43:45.280 --> 00:43:46.239
We want to report a case.

00:43:46.340 --> 00:43:47.099
A homicide case.

00:43:48.840 --> 00:43:49.280
Old Qi!

00:43:49.400 --> 00:43:51.460
The Yangs filed charges against Xiaowei!

00:43:51.719 --> 00:43:52.820
Charges... against me?

